reviewText:
Space Science in Action: Moon DVD Which is same product from schlessinger media for $14.00

Ensure which product is cheaper before you order one.

My 4 year old son knows this video by heart and often asks to go the library to check it out  - again.  He can explain the concepts presented and likes to play the moon and sun game.  So on his behalf, I give this video a 5 stars rating.
